Memon and Ahmad
</taxonomicName>
) to provide clearer delineation of the genera. In the absence of such a study, a conservative approach is to adhere on the original description of 
<bibRefCitation author="Ghauri, M. S. K." box="[455,616,259,285]" pageId="19" pageNumber="302" pagination="9 - 27" refId="ref12389" refString="Ghauri, M. S. K. (1977) Sarju - a new genus of Halyini (Heteroptera, Pentatomidae, Pentatominae) with new species. Tu ¨ rkiye Bitki Koruma Dergisi, 1 (1), 9 - 27." type="journal article" year="1977">Ghauri (1977)</bibRefCitation>
as well as the diagnostics described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Memon, N. &amp; Ahmad, I." box="[1077,1389,259,285]" pageId="19" pageNumber="302" pagination="399 - 411" refId="ref12648" refString="Memon, N. &amp; Ahmad, I. (2009) A revision of halyine stink bug genus Sarju Ghauri (Hemiptera: Pentatomidae: Halyini) and its cladistic analysis. Pakistan Journal of Zoology, 41 (5), 399 - 411." type="journal article" year="2009">Memon and Ahmad (2009)</bibRefCitation>
, the last revision undertaken on 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Ghauri" baseAuthorityYear="1977" box="[459,520,295,321]" class="Insecta" family="Pentatomidae" genus="Sarju" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[459,520,295,321]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="302">Sarju</emphasis>
